Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,designing Swift Playgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For that awesome introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know how to follow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,his jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Elizabeth, and I'm a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,content engineer, writer, and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,storyteller on the Swift
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Playgrounds team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really excited to be here
