Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Playgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's start at the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a Swift Playground?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you, all our scholarship
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,students, know intimately what a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Swift Playground is, because you
