Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Others of you might have played
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,with these, might have learned
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,from one yourself, how the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,beginnings of coding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A Swift Playground is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,essentially a collection of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,pages, like this one.
