Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At the top are the instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the story, whatever concept
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you're trying to get across to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,your learners.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where you're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,teach them what they're about to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,do.
