Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,out what you've taught them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then on the right hand side,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the live view.
